<div class="wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-14cf5ab5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex">
<div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-15ea44a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:60%">		<div class="manitoba-faq-entries wp-block-manitoba-faq-faq-entries" data-accordion-role="group"
			data-accordion-behavior="single">
							<div class="manitoba-faq-item manitoba-faq-item--featured" data-accordion-role="item">
					<p class="manitoba-faq-question">
						<button type="button" id="faq-question-7076" class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger"
							aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-7076">
							<span class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger-label">Où sont stockées les archives ?</span>
						</button>
					</p>
					<div class="manitoba-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-7076"
						aria-labelledby="faq-question-7076" hidden>
						
<p>Dans les datacenters XEFI en France. Chaque archive est dupliquée automatiquement sur un second site.</p>



<p></p>

											</div>
				</div>
							<div class="manitoba-faq-item manitoba-faq-item--featured" data-accordion-role="item">
					<p class="manitoba-faq-question">
						<button type="button" id="faq-question-7092" class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger"
							aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-7092">
							<span class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger-label">Où sont stockées les données ?</span>
						</button>
					</p>
					<div class="manitoba-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-7092"
						aria-labelledby="faq-question-7092" hidden>
						
<p>Dans les datacenters XEFI en France, sécurisés et conformes aux normes les plus strictes (RGPD, HDS…).</p>



<p></p>

											</div>
				</div>
							<div class="manitoba-faq-item manitoba-faq-item--featured" data-accordion-role="item">
					<p class="manitoba-faq-question">
						<button type="button" id="faq-question-7090" class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger"
							aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-7090">
							<span class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger-label">Que sauvegarde-t-on exactement ?</span>
						</button>
					</p>
					<div class="manitoba-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-7090"
						aria-labelledby="faq-question-7090" hidden>
						
<p>Tout : vos données, vos logiciels et la configuration de votre système. En cas de crash, vous pouvez tout restaurer.</p>



<p></p>

											</div>
				</div>
							<div class="manitoba-faq-item manitoba-faq-item--featured" data-accordion-role="item">
					<p class="manitoba-faq-question">
						<button type="button" id="faq-question-7088" class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger"
							aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-7088">
							<span class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger-label">Et si je n’ai pas encore de solution de sauvegarde ?</span>
						</button>
					</p>
					<div class="manitoba-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-7088"
						aria-labelledby="faq-question-7088" hidden>
						
<p>Le PRA nécessite une sauvegarde préalable via XEFI. Nos équipes peuvent vous proposer un pack complet.</p>



<p></p>

											</div>
				</div>
							<div class="manitoba-faq-item manitoba-faq-item--featured" data-accordion-role="item">
					<p class="manitoba-faq-question">
						<button type="button" id="faq-question-7086" class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger"
							aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-7086">
							<span class="manitoba-faq-question-trigger-label">Puis-je tester le fonctionnement du PRA ?</span>
						</button>
					</p>
					<div class="manitoba-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-7086"
						aria-labelledby="faq-question-7086" hidden>
						
<p>Oui, des tests de PRA sont possibles à tout moment. Chaque test est planifié avec nos équipes.</p>



<p></p>

